                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-976" type="given" value="NER"></interp>NER BROWNING</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable E</hi> 59.) I saw the prisoner running</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183906170118"></xptr>
               <p>with this caddy—he threw it down—I ran and took him—I did not lose sight of him till I caught him—I then took the caddy and him to the station-house.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> Where did you take him? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> He went up Dean-street, and then into Eagle-street—I did not lose sight of him—he appeared to be in very bad health—he told me he was under medical advice.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received an excellent character.)</p>
